Section 1246 of the Food Security Act of 1985 (the 1985 Act), as amended by the Agricultural Act of 2014 (2014 Act), requires that implementation of programs authorized by Title XII of the 1985 Act be made without regard to the Paperwork Reduction Act of 1995 (44 U.S.C. 3501 
et seq.
). Therefore, NRCS is not reporting recordkeeping or estimated paperwork burden associated with this interim rule.

