et seq.
). The 2014 Act combined the statutory definition of the National Organic Program into the statutory definition of âorganic system planâ by adding the statutory reference to the definition of âorganic system planâ and removing the separate definition. NRCS maintains the separate definition for the National Organic Program in the regulation for clarification purposes.
